---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Sitios web premium | Presencia Digital"
  description="Diseñamos sitios web a medida que explican claramente tu negocio, generan confianza y convierten visitas en oportunidades."
>
  <div class="swp-page">

    <!-- BREADCRUMB -->
    <nav class="swp-breadcrumb container-libera" aria-label="Navegación de migas de pan">
      <a href="/soluciones">Soluciones</a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
      <a href="/soluciones/presencia-digital">Presencia Digital</a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
      <span aria-current="page">Sitios web premium</span>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="swp-hero">
      <div class="container-libera swp-hero-grid">

        <div class="swp-hero-copy">
          <h1 class="swp-title display-hero">
            Tu sitio web es tu vendedor más constante.
            <em>Trabaja mientras tú no puedes.</em>
          </h1>
          <p class="swp-lead">
            Diseñamos y desarrollamos sitios web a medida para empresas que quieren una presencia digital que genere confianza, explique bien lo que hacen y convierta visitantes en clientes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Mock website preview -->
        <aside class="swp-mock" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="swp-browser">
            <div class="swp-browser-bar">
              <span class="swp-dot swp-dot--red"></span>
              <span class="swp-dot swp-dot--yellow"></span>
              <span class="swp-dot swp-dot--green"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="swp-browser-content">
              <!-- Fake site: NEXORA -->
              <div class="swp-site-nav">
                <span class="swp-site-brand">NEXORA</span>
                <div class="swp-site-links">
                  <span>Servicios ∨</span>
                  <span>Casos de éxito</span>
                  <span>Nosotros</span>
                  <span>Recursos ∨</span>
                </div>
                <span class="swp-site-cta-nav">Contacto</span>
              </div>

              <!-- Hero block -->
              <div class="swp-site-hero">
                <div class="swp-site-hero-copy">
                  <span class="swp-site-eyebrow">Consultoría estratégica</span>
                  <p class="swp-site-headline">Estrategias que impulsan negocios con visión de futuro.</p>
                  <p class="swp-site-sub">Acompañamos a empresas a crecer con claridad, eficiencia y foco en resultados reales.</p>
                  <div class="swp-site-btns">
                    <span class="swp-site-btn-primary">Conocer servicios</span>
                    <span class="swp-site-btn-ghost">Hablar con un asesor</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="swp-site-hero-img"></div>
              </div>

              <!-- Features strip -->
              <div class="swp-site-strip">
                <div class="swp-strip-item">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M8 2L2 6v8h4v-4h4v4h4V6z"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <span>Estrategia clara</span>
                    <span>y accionable</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="swp-strip-item">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><polyline points="2 12 6 7 9 10 14 4"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <span>Enfoque en</span>
                    <span>resultados medibles</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="swp-strip-item">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M8 8a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6z"/><path d="M14 14a6 6 0 0 0-12 0"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <span>Acompañamiento</span>
                    <span>cercano y experto</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="swp-strip-item">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><rect x="2" y="2" width="5" height="5" rx="0.5"/><rect x="9" y="2" width="5" height="5" rx="0.5"/><rect x="2" y="9" width="5" height="5" rx="0.5"/><path d="M9 11.5h5M11.5 9v5"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <span>Soluciones adaptadas</span>
                    <span>a tu negocio</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Process section -->
              <div class="swp-site-process">
                <p class="swp-process-title">Cómo trabajamos</p>
                <p class="swp-process-sub">Un método probado para transformar objetivos en resultados.</p>
                <div class="swp-process-steps">
                  <div class="swp-step">
                    <span class="swp-step-num">01</span>
                    <span class="swp-step-name">Descubrimos</span>
                    <span class="swp-step-desc">Entendemos tu negocio, tus desafíos y tus objetivos.</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="swp-step">
                    <span class="swp-step-num">02</span>
                    <span class="swp-step-name">Estrategia</span>
                    <span class="swp-step-desc">Diseñamos un plan claro con acciones priorizadas.</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="swp-step">
                    <span class="swp-step-num">03</span>
                    <span class="swp-step-name">Ejecución</span>
                    <span class="swp-step-desc">Implementamos con foco en impacto y eficiencia.</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="swp-step">
                    <span class="swp-step-num">04</span>
                    <span class="swp-step-name">Resultados</span>
                    <span class="swp-step-desc">Medimos, optimizamos y escalamos lo que funciona.</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CONTENT -->
    <section class="swp-content">
      <div class="container-libera swp-content-grid">

        <div class="swp-body">
          <p><strong>Un sitio web mal hecho no solo no vende. También descalifica.</strong></p>
          <p>
            En los primeros segundos, tu visitante decide si confía en tu negocio. Si el diseño se ve viejo, la información es confusa, el sitio es lento o no entiende cuál es el siguiente paso, se va.
          </p>
          <p><strong>Construimos sitios que hacen el trabajo opuesto.</strong></p>
          <p>
            Cada sección está pensada para explicar, generar confianza y guiar al siguiente paso. El diseño refleja la calidad de tu negocio y la estructura ayuda a tu visitante a entender qué ofreces, por qué elegirte y cómo contactarte.
          </p>
          <p><strong>Tu sitio está conectado a lo que mueve tu negocio.</strong></p>
          <p>
            Lo conectamos con WhatsApp, formularios, CRM, automatizaciones, métricas y gestión de contenidos para que puedas actualizarlo y mejorarlo sin depender de código.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="swp-features">
          <h2 class="swp-features-title">Lo que construimos</h2>
          <ul class="swp-features-list">
            <li>
              <svg class="swp-feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
              Diseño a medida, sin plantillas disfrazadas.
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg class="swp-feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/></svg>
              Arquitectura de contenido pensada para convertir.
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg class="swp-feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
              Velocidad optimizada para móvil y escritorio.
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg class="swp-feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
              SEO técnico incluido desde la estructura del sitio.
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg class="swp-feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
              Formularios conectados a WhatsApp, correo, CRM o base de datos.
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg class="swp-feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/><line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"/></svg>
              Panel de gestión de contenidos simple para tu equipo.
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg class="swp-feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
              Código original, limpio y fácil de mantener.
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg class="swp-feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/><path d="M14 17.5h7M17.5 14v7"/></svg>
              Base preparada para analítica, automatizaciones e integraciones futuras.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- QUOTE -->
    <section class="swp-quote">
      <div class="container-libera swp-quote-inner">
        <div class="swp-quote-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="26" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 3" opacity="0.3"/>
            <path d="M20 20h24v18H20z" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.5" rx="1"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="26" x2="44" y2="26" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.2" opacity="0.5"/>
            <line x1="24" y1="30" x2="36" y2="30" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.2" opacity="0.4"/>
            <circle cx="40" cy="42" r="8" fill="var(--orange)"/>
            <path d="M37 42l2 2 4-4" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="swp-quote-text">
          Tu sitio explica, filtra, <em>genera confianza</em> y abre conversaciones comerciales.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="swp-cta">
      <div class="container-libera swp-cta-inner">
        <div class="swp-cta-copy">
          <div class="swp-cta-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 80 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <!-- Monitor frame -->
              <rect x="4" y="4" width="52" height="38" rx="2" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <line x1="4" y1="36" x2="56" y2="36" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <line x1="30" y1="42" x2="30" y2="48" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="18" y1="48" x2="42" y2="48" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <!-- Screen content lines -->
              <line x1="10" y1="12" x2="35" y2="12" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.6"/>
              <line x1="10" y1="16" x2="28" y2="16" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.4"/>
              <line x1="10" y1="20" x2="32" y2="20" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.4"/>
              <!-- Image placeholder -->
              <rect x="38" y="10" width="14" height="10" rx="1" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.2" opacity="0.5"/>
              <path d="M38 20l4-4 3 3 2-2 5 3" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.4"/>
              <!-- Plant leaves -->
              <path d="M60 52c0-5 4-9 8-10-1 5-5 9-8 10z" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/>
              <path d="M68 54c0-5-4-9-8-8 1 5 5 8 8 8z" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" opacity="0.4"/>
              <!-- Star badge -->
              <circle cx="60" cy="40" r="8" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="var(--orange)"/>
              <path d="M60 35l1.5 3h3.2l-2.6 1.9 1 3.1-3.1-2.3-3.1 2.3 1-3.1L55.3 38h3.2z" fill="#fff" stroke="none"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="swp-cta-text">
            Un sitio bien construido trabaja por tu negocio las 24 horas: explica, filtra, <em>genera confianza</em> y abre conversaciones comerciales incluso cuando tú no estás disponible.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/diagnostico" class="btn-primary swp-cta-btn">
          Construir mi sitio web
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>

  <style>
    .swp-page {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    /* ── BREADCRUMB ── */
    .swp-breadcrumb {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding-top: calc(var(--nav-height) + 1.25rem);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    .swp-breadcrumb a { color: var(--text-secondary); transition: color 0.2s; }
    .swp-breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--orange); }
    .swp-breadcrumb [aria-current="page"] { color: var(--orange); font-weight: 600; }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .swp-hero {
      padding-top: clamp(4rem, calc(3vw + 2.5rem), 5rem);
      padding-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    }

    .swp-hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1.3fr);
      gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
      align-items: start;
    }


    .swp-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .swp-title em { font-style: normal; color: var(--orange); }

    .swp-lead {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.15vw, 1rem);
      line-height: 1.75;
      max-width: 46ch;
    }

    /* ── BROWSER MOCK ── */
    .swp-mock {
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 40px oklch(0% 0 0 / 0.12);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .swp-browser-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem;
      background: #f0f0f0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .swp-dot {
      display: block;
      width: 0.6rem;
      height: 0.6rem;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .swp-dot--red    { background: #ff5f57; }
    .swp-dot--yellow { background: #febc2e; }
    .swp-dot--green  { background: #28c840; }

    .swp-browser-content {
      background: #fff;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* ── Fake site: NEXORA ── */
    .swp-site-nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .swp-site-brand {
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #003049;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .swp-site-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      color: #555;
      font-size: 0.55rem;
    }

    .swp-site-cta-nav {
      padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
      background: #003049;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 0.2rem;
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .swp-site-hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      padding: 1rem 0.75rem;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .swp-site-hero-copy {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.3rem;
    }

    .swp-site-eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.5rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: #888;
    }

    .swp-site-headline {
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #003049;
      line-height: 1.2;
      max-width: 18ch;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .swp-site-sub {
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.4;
      max-width: 26ch;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .swp-site-btns {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }

    .swp-site-btn-primary {
      padding: 0.25rem 0.55rem;
      background: #003049;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 0.2rem;
      font-size: 0.52rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .swp-site-btn-ghost {
      padding: 0.25rem 0.55rem;
      border: 1px solid #003049;
      color: #003049;
      border-radius: 0.2rem;
      font-size: 0.52rem;
    }

    .swp-site-hero-img {
      width: 6rem;
      height: 4.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, oklch(25% 0.04 235) 0%, oklch(40% 0.04 220) 100%);
      border-radius: 0.25rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .swp-site-hero-img::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 4px,
        oklch(100% 0 0 / 0.04) 4px,
        oklch(100% 0 0 / 0.04) 8px
      );
    }

    .swp-site-strip {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      background: #003049;
      padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .swp-strip-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.3rem;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .swp-strip-item svg {
      width: 0.85rem;
      height: 0.85rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 0.05rem;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .swp-strip-item div {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.05rem;
    }

    .swp-strip-item span:first-child {
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .swp-strip-item span:last-child {
      font-size: 0.5rem;
      opacity: 0.7;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .swp-site-process {
      padding: 0.75rem;
      background: #fafafa;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .swp-process-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0 0 0.1rem;
    }

    .swp-process-sub {
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .swp-process-steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .swp-step {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.15rem;
      padding: 0.4rem;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 0.25rem;
    }

    .swp-step-num {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      color: var(--orange);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .swp-step-name {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .swp-step-desc {
      font-size: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    /* ── CONTENT ── */
    .swp-content {
      padding-block: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      background: #fff;
    }

    .swp-content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 6rem);
      align-items: start;
    }

    .swp-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }

    .swp-body p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.1vw, 1rem);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .swp-body strong { color: var(--text-primary); }

    .swp-features-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .swp-features-list {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.875rem;
    }

    .swp-features-list li {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      align-items: start;
      font-size: 0.975rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .swp-feat-icon {
      width: 1.1rem;
      height: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--orange);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
    }

    /* ── QUOTE ── */
    .swp-quote {
      padding-block: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      background: var(--surface-alt);
    }

    .swp-quote-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.75rem;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin-inline: auto;
      padding: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      background: #fff;
    }

